title: GoPro Awards: Park Jumps with Twin Brothers, Jake and Theo Riddle
description:
Six-year-old twins Jake and Theo Riddle spend the day at Gorge Road Jump Park in Queenstown, New Zealand. 

Captured and submitted by GoPro Awards recipients, Jake and Theo Riddle.

Shot 100% on the HERO4® camera
